<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>职场避坑 on 曹义德律师专栏</title><link>https://caoyide.com/tags/%E8%81%8C%E5%9C%BA%E9%81%BF%E5%9D%91/</link><description>Recent content in 职场避坑 on 曹义德律师专栏</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://caoyide.com/tags/%E8%81%8C%E5%9C%BA%E9%81%BF%E5%9D%91/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>试用期被辞退，有赔偿吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%AF%95%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F%E6%9D%83%E7%9B%8A/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%AF%95%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F%E6%9D%83%E7%9B%8A/</guid><description>试用期不是白用期。公司不能在试用期随便让你走人，不能延长试用期，不能不给工资。</description></item><item><title>离职之后公司不让你去同行上班——竞业限制你该拿多少钱？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E7%AB%9E%E4%B8%9A%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E7%AB%9E%E4%B8%9A%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</guid><description>签了竞业限制协议，离职后两年内不能去同行。但公司每个月要给你补偿金。不给钱？协议自动作废。</description></item><item><title>加班费到底怎么算？很多人被公司忽悠了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%8A%A0%E7%8F%AD%E8%B4%B9/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%8A%A0%E7%8F%AD%E8%B4%B9/</guid><description>工作日加班1.5倍、休息日2倍、法定节假日3倍。你的加班费拿对了吗？</description></item><item><title>上班路上摔了一跤，算不算工伤？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BC%A4%E8%AE%A4%E5%AE%9A/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BC%A4%E8%AE%A4%E5%AE%9A/</guid><description>在上班路上被车撞了算工伤吗？在公司团建时受伤呢？在家加班猝死呢？工伤认定的边界比你想象的宽。</description></item><item><title>公司让你走人，一分钱不赔？这三笔钱你该拿</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%BE%9E%E9%80%80/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%BE%9E%E9%80%80/</guid><description>被辞退的时候，公司该赔你多少钱？经济补偿金、赔偿金、代通知金——三笔钱，很多人一笔都没拿到。</description></item><item><title>公司不跟你签劳动合同？别慌，你赚了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%8C%E5%80%8D%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%90%88%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%8C%E5%80%8D%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84/</guid><description>很多人以为不签劳动合同是公司占便宜。错了，是公司给你送钱——法律规定超过一个月不签合同，每月赔你双倍工资，最多赔11个月。</description></item></channel></rss>